menu "Dome bus configuration"

config DOME_BUS_MUTEX_TIMEOUT_MS
    int "Dome bus mutex timeout (ms)"
    range 0 10000
    default 50
    help
        Timeout in milliseconds for dome bus mutex acquisition. When set to 0 the
        lock will wait indefinitely. A non-zero value causes dome_bus_lock() and
        the read/write helpers to return ESP_ERR_TIMEOUT if the mutex cannot be
        taken within the configured interval.

endmenu
